#WidgetBoard

Logic for creating a board of widgets on the screen.

##Board.js 

contains the logic for handling the board.

###requirements
- underscore

##widgetboard.js

is an example of how to use board.js

###requirements

- underscore
- backbone
- https://github.com/rhysbrettbowen/Backbone.ComponentView : for backbone view managment
- https://github.com/rhysbrettbowen/Backbone.Advice : to handle mixins to make the board movable
- https://github.com/rhysbrettbowen/Backbone.AdviceFactory : to handle inheritance
- https://github.com/rhysbrettbowen/MouseMover : so movement only happens on animationFrame rather than mousemove

